{"tid":2336153,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今年咩事？收到幾個call, 問我有冇興趣轉工","createTime":"2020-12-22T11:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T12:33:55.000Z","uid":21682,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d28106123973ce8bc012f6e7bc08bd3accc1ec7b","tid":2336153,"uid":21682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"現時做緊物管TO<br />\n5 days, 14 AL, 25k<br />\n好多野煩，間唔中有急call返公司，出下tender, 跟下判頭， 樓下有4x個 tech要管，多數忙到仆街，不過間唔中有1至半日都有得係公司R下爛腳<br />\n<br />\n由上個月開始，總共收左3個電話問我轉唔轉工, 可能係以前戇尻尻俾左份 CV head hunt<br />\n<br />\n當中有一份幾吸引<br />\nCBRE, 英國既銀行工程狗 ，3xk，聽HR講，一樣要聽電話接call, 落site, 出tender果d, 聽落好似同而加差唔多咁<br />\n<br />\n其實我係想係到索下料，CBRE既正負皮好似都好兩極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ba8e49b8e9a8ffe32c7944cd140df852154968","tid":2336153,"uid":21682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2ccd73ed833fbb116a9e9f7e13894a041b9105","tid":2336153,"uid":356914,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:35:19.000Z","msg":"睇錢做人"},{"pid":"359761f36ec28262cc36d12076eacae126c753e2","tid":2336153,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:41:45.000Z","msg":"今年真係幾好景"},{"pid":"68df58f07d9090286bcb910e2854e8c18703ae8e","tid":2336153,"uid":21682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"359761f36ec28262cc36d12076eacae126c753e2","tid":2336153,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:41:45.000Z","msg":"今年真係幾好景"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:46:31